HE'S CLEAN AS A WHISTLE.

23:09.480 --> 23:11.084
IF THAT WHISTLE WAS SLIGHTLY
MORALLY REPUGNANT.

23:11.120 --> 23:12.644
SIMMONS: SO THAT CLEARS HIM.

23:12.690 --> 23:14.658
BUT WHY DID THE UNSUB
TARGET KAL TO BEGIN WITH?

23:14.690 --> 23:15.679
KAL'S AMBITIOUS.

23:15.720 --> 23:18.723
HE MUST HAVE KNOWN IT
AND USED IT TO HIS BENEFIT.

23:18.760 --> 23:20.625
SO HE'S SMART ENOUGH
NOT TO EXPOSE HIMSELF,

23:20.660 --> 23:22.525
WHICH IS PROBABLY
NOT EASY FOR SOMEONE

23:22.560 --> 23:23.766
WHO'S DESPERATE
FOR ATTENTION.

23:23.800 --> 23:25.097
GARCIA: ALSO, I HAVE
TO SAY WHOEVER THIS IS

23:25.130 --> 23:26.722
IS, LIKE, A TECH WIZARD.

23:26.770 --> 23:28.658
BECAUSE I HAVE USED
ALL THE TOOLS

23:28.700 --> 23:31.066
IN MY FANTASTIC BOX,
AND HE'S, LIKE, PROTECTED

23:31.110 --> 23:33.635
FROM THE MOTHER ON HIGH
OF ALL ENCRYPTION PACKAGES

23:33.680 --> 23:35.079
AND A SECURE SERVER,

23:35.110 --> 23:36.338
PLUS AN IP SCRAMBLER,

23:36.380 --> 23:39.747
WHICH IS NOT LIKE
THE WARM, EGGY KIND
BUT THE COMPUTERY KIND.

23:39.780 --> 23:42.943
SO YOU'VE GOT NOTHING
ON THE UNSUB'S I.D.
AND LOCATION?

23:42.980 --> 23:44.982
NO. I MEAN,
ACCORDING TO MY SCREENS,

23:45.020 --> 23:46.612
IT'S ALL COMING
FROM JAMAICA.

23:46.650 --> 23:48.049
KINGSTON,
TO BE EXACT.

23:48.090 --> 23:49.614
IT DOES NOT TAKE
A PROFILER TO KNOW

23:49.660 --> 23:51.059
THAT'S COMPLETELY BOGUS.

23:51.090 --> 23:52.648
WELL, IF HE REACHED OUT
TO CHANNEL 3,

23:52.690 --> 23:53.952
THEN HE MIGHT HAVE TO
OTHER NEWS OUTLETS, TOO.

23:54.000 --> 23:55.922
GARCIA, DID HE SEND
THE VIDEOS TO ANYBODY ELSE?

23:55.960 --> 23:58.064
JUST--JUST KAL
AT CHANNEL 3. THAT'S IT.

23:58.100 --> 23:59.727
IF THE UNSUB
IS FOCUSED ON THEM,

23:59.770 --> 24:01.465
HE MUST HAVE A PERSONAL
CONNECTION THERE.

24:01.500 --> 24:03.730
GARCIA, LOOK INTO FORMER
CHANNEL 3 EMPLOYEES,

24:03.770 --> 24:05.658
SEE IF ANY OF THEM
FIT THE PROFILE.

24:05.710 --> 24:07.632
COPY, COPY.

24:07.680 --> 24:10.001
YOU KNOW WHAT BOTHERS ME
ABOUT THIS GUY?

24:10.040 --> 24:12.702
IS IT THE FACT THAT KAL
MIGHT WIN A LOCAL NEWS
EMMY OFF HIM?

24:12.750 --> 24:15.674
CLOSE. IT'S THAT
WITH EACH CRIME SCENE,

24:15.720 --> 24:16.971
THE WINDOW BETWEEN
THE MURDER

24:17.020 --> 24:19.739
AND THE START
OF FILMING, IT SHRINKS.

24:19.790 --> 24:20.984
RIGHT?
AND AT SOME POINT,

24:21.020 --> 24:22.681
THAT'S GONNA CONVERGE.

24:22.720 --> 24:26.121
OK, WE PROFILED
HE WAS GOING
FOR A BIGGER BANG.

24:27.190 --> 24:29.829
HE'S GONNA MAKE
A SNUFF FILM.

24:36.240 --> 24:38.504
WOMAN: OVER HERE!
OVER HERE!

24:38.540 --> 24:40.531
MAN: RIGHT HERE, KID!
LOOK AT ME!

24:40.580 --> 24:42.275
[CAMERAS FLASHING]

24:42.310 --> 24:44.005
[REPORTERS SHOUTING AT ONCE]

24:44.050 --> 24:46.644
MAN: ARE YOU OK?

25:29.090 --> 25:30.626
[TAP TAP]

25:30.660 --> 25:32.787
WHAT THE HELL?

25:34.000 --> 25:34.694
[GUNSHOT]

25:45.070 --> 25:47.163
THANK YOU FOR COMING
SO FAST.

25:47.210 --> 25:48.029
WE DIDN'T EXPECT YOU
TO CALL.

25:48.080 --> 25:49.809
WELL, NOW THAT I KNOW
THAT KAL'S SOURCE

25:49.840 --> 25:51.046
IS THE KILLER, I HAD TO.

25:51.080 --> 25:53.002
DID YOU OR KAL
WATCH THE NEW VIDEO?

25:53.050 --> 25:55.245
I DID. IT'S BRUTAL.

26:25.180 --> 26:27.876
SANDRA: PLEASE TELL
ME THAT LITTLE GIRL
IS STILL ALIVE.

26:27.920 --> 26:30.047
ALVEZ: THERE'S NOT
MUCH TO GO ON HERE.

26:30.080 --> 26:33.015
THERE'S NO SIGNAGE,
BUILDINGS.

26:33.050 --> 26:35.109
YOU CAN'T SEE THE PLATES
ON THE CAR.

26:35.160 --> 26:36.787
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW
THEIR NAMES.

26:36.820 --> 26:38.879
BUT WE DO HAVE
GEOGRAPHY.

26:41.300 --> 26:43.359
YOU SEE THIS?

26:43.400 --> 26:47.097
WELL, THE CEMENT
LAMP POST IN THE BACK.

26:47.130 --> 26:50.236
IT'S TALL, LIKE AT
A MALL PARKING LOT.

26:50.270 --> 26:52.033
BUT THOSE ARE
ALL ACROSS THE CITY.

26:52.070 --> 26:53.401
THEY COULD HAVE BEEN
ANYWHERE.

26:53.440 --> 26:55.135
YEAH, BUT WE KNOW
THE UNSUB'S COMFORT ZONE.

26:55.180 --> 26:56.829
GARCIA: WHAT'S UP?

26:56.880 --> 26:58.199
GARCIA, HOW MANY
SHOPPING AND STRIP MALLS

26:58.250 --> 27:00.002
ARE INSIDE THE UNSUB'S
HUNTING GROUNDS?

27:01.720 --> 27:04.917
5.
WE NEED ALL 5.
WE'LL SPLIT UP.

27:08.090 --> 27:11.150
[SIREN]

27:33.210 --> 27:34.973
HI, SWEETIE.

27:35.020 --> 27:36.214
I'M JENNIFER.

27:36.250 --> 27:38.241
IS SOMEBODY COMING
TO HELP NANCY?

27:38.290 --> 27:41.817
YEAH. YEAH.
LET'S GET YOU HOME.

27:41.860 --> 27:44.124
I WANT MY MOM AND DAD.

27:44.160 --> 27:47.721
EVERYTHING'S GONNA
BE OK. DON'T WORRY.

27:47.760 --> 27:50.354
[SIRENS]

27:54.170 --> 27:55.797
ALVEZ: HOW IS SHE DOING?

27:55.840 --> 27:57.432
GOOD, CONSIDERING.

27:57.470 --> 27:58.459
WHAT'S HER NAM E?

27:58.510 --> 28:00.205
ALEX GRAYSON.

28:00.240 --> 28:02.708
THE LATEST VICTIM,
NANCY JONES,

28:02.740 --> 28:04.207
WAS HER COUSIN.

28:04.250 --> 28:06.810
SHE WAS BABYSITTING WHILE
ALEX'S PARENTS WERE OUT.

28:06.850 --> 28:08.442
IT'S A LITTLE LATE TO BE
IN A MALL PARKING LOT

28:08.480 --> 28:10.243
WITH A KID IN THE CAR.

28:10.280 --> 28:12.316
YEAH, WELL,
WHEN A KID CAN'T SLEEP,

28:12.350 --> 28:14.250
A CAR RIDE'S OFTEN
THE BEST WAY
TO GET THEM DOWN.

28:14.290 --> 28:16.178
YEAH, BUT IF ALEX
WAS ASLEEP,

28:16.220 --> 28:17.482
WHY NOT DRIVE
BACK HOME?

28:17.520 --> 28:19.351
SHE PULLED OVER
TO ANSWER A TEXT

28:19.390 --> 28:20.891
FROM A GUY
SHE WAS GONNA MEET.

28:20.930 --> 28:24.297
THERE'S NO WAY NANCY
WAS CHOSEN AT RANDOM.

28:24.330 --> 28:26.218
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE RIGHT.

28:26.270 --> 28:28.135
THIS GUY'S A PLANNER.

28:28.170 --> 28:31.207
HE DOESN'T DO RANDOM.
HE MUST HAVE STALKED HER.

28:31.240 --> 28:34.778
AND IF HE DID,
THEN HE KNEW THERE
WAS A KID IN THE CAR.

28:34.810 --> 28:38.974
THE QUESTION 15--
AND I HATE TO ASK--

28:39.010 --> 28:41.217
WHY IS ALEX
STILL ALIVE?

28:41.250 --> 28:44.287
I DON'T KNOW. HE'S NEVER
SHOWN A MORAL COMPASS,

28:44.320 --> 28:45.480
SO WHY NOW?

28:45.520 --> 28:47.852
MAYBE THE UNSUB'S
A DAD.

28:47.890 --> 28:50.415
OR MAYBE SOMETHING
HAPPENED TO HIM
WHEN HE WAS LITTLE.

28:50.460 --> 28:52.348
THIS WAY.

28:52.390 --> 28:54.824
FATHER: AGENT JAREAU,
THANK YOU SO MUCH

28:54.860 --> 28:55.895
FOR FINDING
OUR LITTLE GIRL.

28:55.930 --> 28:57.295
OF COURSE.

29:07.510 --> 29:09.398
[INDISTINCT CHATTER OUTSIDE]

29:13.920 --> 29:17.378
[REPORTERS ALL TALKING AT ONCE]

29:17.420 --> 29:19.342
MAN: THIS WAY, PLEASE!
ALEX?

29:19.390 --> 29:21.210
[CHATTER CONTINUES]

29:21.260 --> 29:23.216
WAIT A MINUTE.

29:29.260 --> 29:31.467
THAT'S IT.

29:31.500 --> 29:34.060
WHEN ROSSI AND I
WERE AT CHANNEL 3,

29:34.100 --> 29:35.465
WE SAW SANDRA'S
WALL OF FAME.

29:35.500 --> 29:37.536
ON IT, THERE WAS
A LITTLE BOY AND HIS FATHER

29:37.570 --> 29:39.333
IN ROUGHLY
THE SAME POSITION.

29:39.370 --> 29:41.372
LIKE RECENTLY?

29:41.410 --> 29:43.799
NO, IT HAD TO HAVE BEEN
20 YEARS AGO AT LEAST,

29:43.850 --> 29:46.842
BUT THERE MIGHT BE
A CONNECTION.

29:46.880 --> 29:48.916
HEY, GARCIA, I NEED YOU
TO CHECK ON

29:48.950 --> 29:50.247
AN OLD CASE IN MIAMI.

29:50.280 --> 29:51.884
FINGERS AT THE READY.

29:51.920 --> 29:54.218
OK, UH, 20 YEARS AGO,

29:54.260 --> 29:56.387
A BOY, ROUGHLY 5 OR 6,

29:56.420 --> 29:58.024
SAW HIS MOM KILLED.

29:58.060 --> 30:01.996
UH, NOTHING IS COMING UP.
THIS IS PRE-INTERNET.

30:02.030 --> 30:03.224
THIS WOULD HAVE RECEIVED

30:03.260 --> 30:05.160
A LOT OF MEDIA
ATTENTION, EVEN BACK THEN.

30:05.200 --> 30:07.225
WE SAID MATERNAL FIGURE
IN THE PROFILE, GARCIA.

30:07.270 --> 30:09.158
TRY BABYSITTER.

30:09.200 --> 30:10.565
I MEAN, ALL OF THESE WOMEN
LOOK MORE LIKE BABYSITTERS,

30:10.600 --> 30:12.067
DON'T YOU THINK?

30:12.110 --> 30:14.078
OK...

30:14.110 --> 30:15.600
20 YEARS AGO THIS MONTH.

30:15.640 --> 30:18.006
THE BOY'S NAME
WAS JEFFERY WHITFIELD.

30:18.050 --> 30:20.245
HE SAW HIS BABYSITTER,
GINA MEADOWS,

30:20.280 --> 30:22.077
MURDERED WITH...

30:22.120 --> 30:23.348
OH, MY.

30:23.380 --> 30:24.916
A .44.

30:24.950 --> 30:27.510
YEAH. SHE WAS
SHOT ONCE IN THE HEART.

30:27.550 --> 30:29.256
JUST LIKE
THE VICTIMS NOW.

30:29.290 --> 30:31.178
JEFFERY AND GINA WERE FOUND
IN A CAR, WEREN'T THEY?

30:31.230 --> 30:33.221
UH-HUH. IN A STRIP MALL
PARKING LOT.

30:33.260 --> 30:35.319
WAS IT INSIDE THE UNSUB'S
COMFORT ZONE?

30:35.360 --> 30:37.920
YEAH, THEY WERE OUTSIDE
THE VET'S OFFICE.

30:37.970 --> 30:40.621
THEY WERE TAKING JEFFERY'S
CAT TO THE VET.

30:40.670 --> 30:42.160
JEFFERY WAS IN THE BACKSEAT.

30:42.200 --> 30:43.360
HE SAW THE WHOLE THING.

30:43.400 --> 30:44.867
HE WASN'T HURT, BUT...

30:44.910 --> 30:47.401
THE VICTIMS BEAR A STRIKING
RESEMBLANCE TO GINA.

30:47.440 --> 30:48.976
I'M SENDING THE INFO NOW.

30:49.010 --> 30:50.602
ALL RIGHT,
THAN KS, GARCIA.

30:54.280 --> 30:57.340
THAT IS OUR UNSUB--
JEFFERY WHITFIELD AT AGE 6.

30:57.380 --> 30:58.984
JEFFERY WAS IN THE CAR
THAT DAY.

30:59.020 --> 31:01.955
THEY CAUGHT THE GUY
DOWN THE ROAD, BUT...

31:01.990 --> 31:03.355
CHECK THIS OUT.

31:03.390 --> 31:06.587
GINA WAS WEARING
THE SAME HAIR CLIP THAT DAY.

31:06.630 --> 31:09.292
THE SAME ONE
HE'S BEEN PLACING
IN HIS VICTIMS' HAIR.

31:09.330 --> 31:11.025
JJ: SANDRA WORKED JEFFERY'S
STORY WHEN IT BROKE,

31:11.070 --> 31:13.630
AND SHE GOT HIS ONLY
ON-CAMERA INTERVIEW
A YEAR LATER.

31:13.670 --> 31:15.535
THAT EXPLAINS
HIS FOCUS ON CHANNEL 3.

31:15.570 --> 31:17.094
HE PROBABLY FELT EXPLOITED.

31:17.140 --> 31:18.368
ALVEZ: OR THE OPPOSITE.

31:18.410 --> 31:20.537
THIS COULD HAVE BEEN
HIS SHINING MOMENT,

31:20.570 --> 31:23.107
THE ONLY TIME HE'S EVER
FELT IMPORTANT BEFORE.

31:23.140 --> 31:25.301
IN A SINGLE-EVENT
IMPRINT,

31:25.350 --> 31:27.306
PEOPLE CAN HAVE
POLAR RESPONSES.

31:27.350 --> 31:30.012
SOME AVOID IT
ENTIRELY; OTHERS
OBSESS OVER IT.

31:30.050 --> 31:32.314
BOTH OF HIS PARENTS
DIED LAST YEAR.

31:32.350 --> 31:35.615
SO TO HIM, THERE'S ONLY
ONE OTHER PERSON
WHO RECALLS THAT DAY.

31:35.660 --> 31:37.355
SANDRA MADSEN.

31:37.390 --> 31:39.324
PRENTISS: HE CREATED
THE STORY,

31:39.360 --> 31:40.679
HOPING TO GET
HER ATTENTION AGAIN,

31:40.730 --> 31:42.322
JUST LIKE HE DID
20 YEARS AGO.

31:42.360 --> 31:44.362
IN HIS MIND,
BOTH HE AND SANDRA

31:44.400 --> 31:45.662
BENEFITED FROM THAT DAY.

31:45.700 --> 31:47.361
SHE GOT HER BIG STORY

31:47.400 --> 31:49.038
AND JEFFERY GOT
HIS MOMENT IN THE SUN.

31:49.070 --> 31:51.129
HE MUST HAVE FIGURED THEY
CAN DO IT ALL AGAIN.

31:51.170 --> 31:52.660
BUT IF SHE STOPS
RUNNING HIS FOOTAGE,

31:52.710 --> 31:54.507
HE COULD SEE THAT
AS A BETRAYAL.

31:54.540 --> 31:56.201
ROSSI: AND JEFFERY
MIGHT JUMP OFF SCRIPT

31:56.240 --> 31:57.673
AND ATTACK HER NEXT.

31:57.710 --> 31:59.405
SANDRA'S PHONE
WENT TO VOICEMAIL.

31:59.450 --> 32:01.213
HE MIGHT HAVE ALREADY
GOTTEN TO HER.

32:01.250 --> 32:02.649
JJ, LUKE, TAKE
JEFFERY'S APARTMENT.

32:02.680 --> 32:04.989
MATT, GET DETECTIVE
WALLENBERG AND
HEAD TO SANDRA'S.

32:05.020 --> 32:07.318
DAVE, YOU AND I WILL
GO TO THE CHANNEL 3
NEWS ROOM.

32:07.350 --> 32:12.458
[INDISTINCT NEWS REPORTS]

32:18.330 --> 32:20.218
WHERE IS IT?

32:22.240 --> 32:24.561
COME ON, SANDRA.
WHERE IS IT?!

32:24.610 --> 32:27.204
NO, NO, NO!

32:27.240 --> 32:28.935
[GRUNTING]

32:43.320 --> 32:45.254
I WANT TO KEEP
THE MOMENTUM GOING,

32:45.290 --> 32:46.518
SO, YEAH, LET'S LEAD
WITH THAT ONE THERE

32:46.560 --> 32:49.097
AND THEN GO OVER
TO THIS ONE HERE.

32:54.540 --> 32:55.768
[GUNSHOTS]

32:55.800 --> 32:58.268
MAN: GET DOWN! GET DOWN!

32:58.310 --> 32:59.265
GUN! GUN!

32:59.310 --> 33:02.131
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]

33:11.150 --> 33:12.481
[GASPING]

33:12.520 --> 33:14.408
DON'T DO THIS.

33:14.460 --> 33:16.758
WHY DID YOU STOP RUNNING
OUR STORY?

33:29.540 --> 33:33.260
[MOANING]

33:33.310 --> 33:35.505
[GASPS]

33:35.540 --> 33:37.132
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

33:37.180 --> 33:39.705
YOU DON'T REMEMBER
ME, DO YOU?

33:41.750 --> 33:43.775
JEFFERY WHITFIELD.

33:46.190 --> 33:48.351
HI, SANDRA.

33:48.390 --> 33:49.709
JEFFERY?

33:49.760 --> 33:52.786
WE WORKED WELL TOGETHER
20 YEARS AGO.

33:52.830 --> 33:55.822
THEN TIME FORGOT
US BOTH.

33:55.860 --> 33:58.067
YOU'RE KILLING PEOPLE.

33:58.100 --> 34:01.763
WE WERE FINALLY GETTING
THE ATTENTION WE DESERVED,

34:01.800 --> 34:03.336
BUT THEN
YOU SCREWED IT UP

34:03.370 --> 34:05.099
BY NOT AIRING
THE LAST MURDER.

34:05.140 --> 34:06.562
JEFFERY, I COULDN'T.

34:06.610 --> 34:07.565
WHY NOT?

34:07.610 --> 34:09.771
THERE WAS A LITTLE GIRL.

34:09.810 --> 34:12.847
I'D NEVER HURT A CHILD.

34:12.880 --> 34:14.677
I'M NOT A MONSTER.

34:14.720 --> 34:16.676
THE WAY YOU CUT
THE FOOTAGE,

34:16.720 --> 34:19.211
I--I DIDN'T KNOW
IF SHE WAS--

34:19.250 --> 34:21.753
IT'S CALLED
A CLIFFHANGER, SANDRA.

34:43.380 --> 34:44.699
OH, GOD.

34:44.750 --> 34:46.604
TELL EVERYONE YOUR NAME.

34:49.320 --> 34:51.185
SANDRA.

34:51.220 --> 34:52.812
SANDRA WHO?

34:55.760 --> 34:57.455
SANDRA MADSEN.

34:58.730 --> 35:00.129
OH, NO. OH, NO.

35:00.160 --> 35:01.650
PRENTISS:
YEAH, GARCIA?

35:01.700 --> 35:03.895
JEFFERY WHITFIELD IS ON--
AND HE'S GOT A--
HE'S GOT A GUN

35:03.930 --> 35:06.364
TO SANDRA'S HEAD, AND HE'S
POSTING IT ALL
ON HIS SOCIAL MEDIA.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.822
PENELOPE, CAN YOU SEE
WHERE THEY ARE?

35:07.870 --> 35:09.394
UH, IN THE NEWS ROOM.

35:09.440 --> 35:11.305
CAN YOU CUT OFF
HIS FEED?

35:11.340 --> 35:12.409
I DON'T THINK
HE'LL KILL SANDRA

35:12.440 --> 35:13.634
IF THE WORLD
CAN'T WATCH.

35:13.670 --> 35:15.672
I CAN TRY, BUT IT'S
GONNA TAKE A SECOND.

35:15.710 --> 35:17.302
PRENTISS:
PLEASE WORK QUICKLY.

35:17.340 --> 35:20.241
I CLOCKED MULTIPLE ENTRANCES
INTO THE NEWS ROOM.

35:20.280 --> 35:21.679
OK, YOU TAKE ONE,
I'LL TAKE ANOTHER.

35:21.720 --> 35:24.416
WE'LL SURROUND HIM
BEST WE CAN.

35:24.450 --> 35:27.886
AND WHAT'S YOUR JOB,
SANDRA MADSEN?

35:27.920 --> 35:32.459
I'M THE NEWS DIRECTOR
AT CHANNEL 3.

35:32.490 --> 35:35.618
ONE OF YOUR FIRST STORIES
WAS ABOUT JEFFERY WHITFIELD,

35:35.660 --> 35:38.458
A BOY WHO SAW
HIS BABYSITTER MURDERED.

35:38.500 --> 35:41.890
DO YOU REMEMBER HIM?

35:41.940 --> 35:44.431
I DO. I DO, JEFFERY.

35:44.470 --> 35:46.700
TELL THEM ABOUT
JEFFERY'S CAT.

35:50.240 --> 35:51.468
PLEASE. I CAN'T.

35:51.510 --> 35:54.877
TELL THEM ABOUT THE CAT.

35:56.950 --> 36:00.613
AI-TER GINA WAS KILLED...

36:00.650 --> 36:05.485
JEFFERY'S CAT LICKED THE
BLOOD OFF OF JEFFERY.

36:05.530 --> 36:07.919
HE DIDN'T SPEAK
FOR ALMOST A YEAR,

36:07.960 --> 36:10.827
TILL I INTERVIEWED
HIM AND...

36:10.860 --> 36:12.566
[SIGHS]

36:12.600 --> 36:15.364
WHEN HE SAW HIMSELF IN
THE CAMERA'S PLAYBACK,

36:15.400 --> 36:19.837
IT WAS...LIKE A GAME.

36:19.870 --> 36:22.668
AND IT WAS MORE FUN
THAN REAL LIFE,

36:22.710 --> 36:26.407
AND IT GOT HIM
COMMUNICATING AGAIN AND--

36:26.450 --> 36:27.906
PRENTISS: FBI!
DROP YOUR WEAPON.

36:27.950 --> 36:29.508
PUT THE GUN DOWN, NOW.

36:29.550 --> 36:32.485
DROP IT, JEFFERY,
NOW! PUT IT DOWN.

36:34.020 --> 36:35.885
[SANDRA GASPS]

36:37.520 --> 36:38.521
NO.

36:38.560 --> 36:40.858
THE WORLD WILL SEE THIS.

36:43.330 --> 36:46.720
AND THEY'LL NEVER
FORGET ME AGAIN.

36:48.640 --> 36:50.892
NO. NO.

36:53.440 --> 36:55.670
NOT TODAY, SATAN!

36:57.740 --> 36:59.799
NO, NO.

36:59.850 --> 37:01.442
IT'S NOT RIGHT
IF IT DOESN'T WORK.

37:01.480 --> 37:03.016
IT HAS TO WORK!

37:03.050 --> 37:04.984
YOU DON'T HAVE
AN AUDIENCE, JEFFERY.

37:07.050 --> 37:09.280
BUT I HAVE TO MAKE
THEM REMEMBER.

37:09.320 --> 37:10.856
BUT IF YOU
WALK AWAY NOW,

37:10.890 --> 37:13.984
THINK ABOUT ALL THE
ATTENTION YOU'LL GET.

37:14.030 --> 37:15.497
THAT'S NOT ENOUGH.

37:15.530 --> 37:17.851
PRENTISS:
RATINGS THROUGH THE ROOF.

37:17.900 --> 37:20.391
ALL THOSE LIKES,
ALL THOSE SHARES.

37:20.430 --> 37:22.364
THE WHOLE WORLD WILL
BE BUZZING ABOUT YOU.

37:22.400 --> 37:25.631
ROSSI: IT'LL BE
THE TRIAL OF THE CENTURY.

37:25.670 --> 37:28.002
PEOPLE WILL FORGET.

37:28.040 --> 37:30.736
THEY ALWAYS DO.

37:30.780 --> 37:34.841
TH EY ALWAYS
FORGET ME.

37:34.880 --> 37:37.041
PRENTISS: JEFFERY, IF YOU
PUT THAT GUN DOWN RIGHT NOW

37:37.080 --> 37:41.449
AND COME WITH US,
WE'LL MAKE SURE NO ONE
EVER FORGETS YOU AGAIN.

37:41.490 --> 37:43.754
HOW?

37:43.790 --> 37:48.022
WE WILL GET YOU A PRIMETIME
BROADCAST NETWORK INTERVIEW.

37:48.060 --> 37:50.028
OK? ONE ON ONE.

37:50.060 --> 37:52.824
NO DISTRACT IONS.
IT'LL ALL BE ABOUT YOU.

37:52.870 --> 37:56.567
AND THEN EVERYBODY
WILL TALK ABOUT IT

37:56.600 --> 37:58.568
FOREVER.

38:13.550 --> 38:15.757
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR BACK.

38:15.790 --> 38:17.849
OK.

38:19.730 --> 38:22.722
[CRYING]

38:22.760 --> 38:25.422
YOU'RE GONNA BE OK.

38:25.470 --> 38:28.735
JEFFERY WHITFIELD,
YOU MAY BE A WIZARD,

38:28.770 --> 38:31.933
BUT I AM AN ORACLE
OF THE HIGHEST ORDER.

38:31.970 --> 38:33.062
[SIGHS]

38:33.110 --> 38:36.932
[INDISTINCT CHATTER OUTSIDE]

38:38.580 --> 38:41.003
THANK YOU, AGENT ROSSI.

38:41.050 --> 38:42.745
HOW YOU HOLDING UP?

38:42.780 --> 38:46.011
I ALWAYS WONDER WHAT
A VICTIM MUST FEEL LIKE

38:46.050 --> 38:49.759
IN THAT MOMENT,
HOW TERRIFYING IT MUST BE.

38:49.790 --> 38:51.587
AND NOW YOU KNOW.

38:51.630 --> 38:54.554
EXCEPT IT WASN'T
TERRIFYING.

38:56.730 --> 38:59.119
IT WAS EXHILARATING.

38:59.170 --> 39:01.468
HE ALMOST KILLED YOU.

39:01.500 --> 39:03.661
BUT HE DIDN'T.

39:03.700 --> 39:05.031
AND NOW THIS.

39:06.910 --> 39:10.471
SANDRA,
THAT'S NOT REAL.

39:10.510 --> 39:12.705
YES, IT IS.

39:12.750 --> 39:17.141
THAT'S WHY I AM
SO GRATEFUL TO JEFFERY.

39:17.180 --> 39:20.638
THE NEXT TIME YOU SEE
HIM, WILL YOU...

39:22.990 --> 39:25.550
WILL YOU THANK HIM FOR ME?

39:30.660 --> 39:34.061
[REPORTERS
ALL SHOUTING QUESTIONS]

39:36.170 --> 39:37.831
SANDRA: TRAGICALLY,

39:37.870 --> 39:40.168
I MET JEFFERY WHITFIELD
20 YEARS AGO.

39:40.210 --> 39:42.770
I WAS A FIELD REPORTER
STARTING OUT,

39:42.810 --> 39:45.142
AND I HAD BEEN ASSIGNED
TO THE SCENE OF A MURDER.

39:45.180 --> 39:47.944
A YOUNG WOMAN HAD BEEN
SHOT AND KILLED...

39:47.980 --> 39:50.016
ROSSI: "I NEVER TRAVEL
WITHOUT MY DIARY.

39:50.050 --> 39:53.417
"ONE SHOULD ALWAYS HAVE
SOMETHING SENSATIONAL TO READ

39:53.450 --> 39:54.951
IN THE TRAIN."

39:54.990 --> 39:55.979
OSCAR WILDE.
